	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hi everyone it's me again. Last time I forgot to log in.&nbsp;&nbsp;anyways hers some more tips. <br><br>10-12  Now you have enough mana that you can try rooting and nuking solo. I personally would get someone to take you up to HHK (HIghhold Keep) and buy a couple of your pet seplls so you don't have to make frequent trips.  If you want to solo you probably should do this,(just don't go through Kicthor Forest at night like I did!!!!)  I was soloing yellow scarbs in the Desert of Ro but you can hunt in NRO, BB/Chessboard, Blackburrow, PLains of Karana/West, Crshbone(DON'T bad faction with dark elves and even if your a lightie I would'nt sugguest it), and Steamfont are all good places that aren't far from most enchanter cities.  <br><br>Fighting Blues- These just get hit your mob once and have pet jump on him and you can nuke it about twice. If your pet is about to die cast fear on the target nuke it then sit down and med. If more then one joins you have 2 choices. If its blue try mezzing and if it fails maybe you should run, if it's even or above I would flee but if you think your ready try it.<br><br>Fighting Evens and Yellows- Buff you and your pet with everything, (even see invisible if your on a PvP server, people sometimes will attack you during while your fighting especially backstabbing rogues) then start out with Root and nuke and nuke and nuke when root wears off you can let him attack you to get pet on him or recast root or mez.  Either way your probably low on mana so you may want to med.  Be careful about your pet cause it may die and I have had many expierances getting critical hits from monsters attacking me while i med.  Just the stradegy here is root nuke debuff if you want and repeat.  It's not as hard as it looks just don't try it on things that use to be red on your last level.  <br><br>Equip- My enchanter is twinked so this is easier for me than yo0. Save up for gossimar if you can or damask.  If your really rich buy a Flowing black robe.  I have a green silken drape which is pretty nice for 200-250 plat.  At this point you may want to get some starting ingredients for our special enchanter only quest. Stein of Moggok.  read more about it on the site and don't try to turn stuff in unless your a dark elf.  Anyways let me get my enchanter to level 12 and i'll give you some more tips!<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Terinan Iceforest</td></tr>
