	   <tr><td colspan=2>Im a lvl 21 enchanter and this is my first character most tell me that im very brave to start of this game with an enchanter thing is im lvl 21 and half of the spells on my book i dont use them when i group i tashan the enemy i cast quickness on the tanks then i cast feckres might or something. . .and then i nuke if there is enough mana. if thing get out of control i mezmeration the whole mob of monsters and med for there is no mana left. . . is there anyone that can give me some advice on what spells should i use when in a group? pls use complete name for spells couse i dont know them all. will apreciate the help. <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
