	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ever since i first logged into Everquest i hated the numberpad setup, because my hand's&nbsp;&nbsp;just too close to the mouse, so i changed it to the default FPS kind. W (forward) A (Strafe left or turn) S (backwards) D (Strafe right)<br>I use F for nearest NPC, G for nearest NPC<br>Q for change view, Forgot what i used E for... Oh yeah, auto run, but that's pretty useless.. <br>oh, Z is auto attack =) <br><br>It works like a charm, because all i have to do is tap my fingures upwards and the're tashed, mezzed, and dead =D<br>Everything else should fall into place, and  BTW the thing is called a "Hotbox"<br>-<br>Velitcia Netcaster, Level 35 Enchanter<br>Cazic-Thule<br>&lt;Path Of Valor&gt;<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
