	   <tr><td colspan=2>this is a strat. for you lvl26-29 people.&nbsp;&nbsp;Most chanters go and find their own little group in ill omen to just sit back and mez all the extra sarnaks in the fort (yes, hunt in the fort at ill omen for this lvl, dont hunt giants).  Well, i tell you no.  Find a tank that is lvl 26+ and PARTNER with him, dont make a group larger than three people, just a waste of exp.  when he pulls give him a alacrity and start melee.  If you are a higher lvl than ur partner, the sarnak wont hit u, and u can screw up the sarnak's hits.  also, i have found a nifty combo, color stun, color shift.  they are stun spells that u get at lvl 4 and 20 (color shift you have to research =( ).  These two spells are low mana spells, and they stun for 4 and 6 secs. you can rotate them for about the hole fight and only loose 15-20% of ur mana, and the tank hasnt been hit yet! just a nifty little thing that i just fould useful. <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
